Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corp&lt;HKBH.HK> is close to a deal on the sale of a commercialbuilding in Hong Kong's Mongkok business district, a bankspokesman said.    He said the 21-storey Wayfoong Plaza was likely to be soldfor about 280 mln H.K. Dlrs but declined to identify the buyer.    The spokesman gave no further details. REUTER&#3;